    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">《Stellar Rhythm》是一款高能量、实验性的横版太空射击游戏，在这里声音与画面交织碰撞。游戏中的一切都与音乐紧密结合：你的飞船武器随节奏开火，敌人完美同步攻击，而充满活力、不断变化的场景会随着节拍扭曲和脉动。甚至你的必杀技不仅带来毁灭性打击 - 还能实时重混原声带，让战场成为一件有生命的乐器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280990/extras/043c87be01684cb4a0c7484cd7d9e9fc.poster.avif?t=1770110102\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280990/extras/043c87be01684cb4a0c7484cd7d9e9fc.webm?t=1770110102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280990/extras/043c87be01684cb4a0c7484cd7d9e9fc.mp4?t=1770110102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">为了实现沉浸感，《Stellar Rhythm》以 120fps 流畅运行，将玩家包裹在色彩、节奏与爆炸动作的万花筒之中。多种游戏模式、深度进程与可解锁的升级，使每一次游戏都是一段全新的声光之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280990/extras/c0e37f875f69e52cb54a528eb56845f1.poster.avif?t=1770110102\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280990/extras/c0e37f875f69e52cb54a528eb56845f1.webm?t=1770110102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280990/extras/c0e37f875f69e52cb54a528eb56845f1.mp4?t=1770110102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">本作由独立开发者 - 屡获殊荣的 DJ 与音乐制作人 Azido 88 - 独立完成，将数十年的地下音乐文化与能量注入独特、实验性的游戏体验。这不仅是一款射击游戏，也不仅是一款音乐游戏: 它是一场迷幻的视听之旅，突破两个类型的界限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280990/extras/548aeb764fd4235bf3f8a2874ca7861f.poster.avif?t=1770110102\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280990/extras/548aeb764fd4235bf3f8a2874ca7861f.webm?t=1770110102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280990/extras/548aeb764fd4235bf3f8a2874ca7861f.mp4?t=1770110102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">原声带涵盖全球地下音乐：从原始的鼓打贝斯与断拍，到强劲的电子、催眠的浩室、震撼的 Dubstep、低音厚重的嘻哈，以及轻松的 Lo-fi 节拍。每一首曲目都推动着音乐与玩法的无缝融合。</p>",
